---
---

<header id="top" class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/90 backdrop-blur">
  <nav class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
    <a href="/" class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-300">
      BuiltByPCB
    </a>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm font-semibold">
      <a href="/" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-cyan-300">Home</a>
      <a href="/case-studies" class="text-cyan-300">Case Studies</a>
      <a href="/resume" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-cyan-300">Resume</a>
      <a href="/projects" class="text-slate-300 transition hover:text-cyan-300">Projects</a>
      <a href="/#contact" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-cyan-300">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </nav>
</header>

<main class="bg-slate-950 px-6 py-12 text-slate-100 md:py-16">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-300">
      Incident Response Case Study
    </p>

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-5xl">
      Coordinating incident response in a mission-critical operational environment.
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300">
      Example of operational coordination, escalation management,
      communication discipline, and resilience support within a
      high-availability aviation surveillance environment.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-4xl space-y-8">

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-300">
        Operational Context
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-300">
        Supported a globally distributed aviation surveillance environment
        operating within a 24/7 mission-critical framework where uptime,
        communication clarity, and escalation discipline directly impacted
        operational continuity.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-300">
        Challenge
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-300">
        High-priority incidents required rapid triage, accurate communication,
        escalation coordination, and operational stabilization across multiple
        technical stakeholders while maintaining audit-quality documentation
        and minimizing service disruption.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-300">
        Actions Taken
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-slate-300">
        <p>
          Coordinated incident escalation and communication between operational,
          engineering, and stakeholder teams.
        </p>

        <p>
          Assisted with incident prioritization, response tracking,
          and procedural alignment during operational disruptions.
        </p>

        <p>
          Maintained structured incident documentation to support
          operational accountability and post-incident analysis.
        </p>

        <p>
          Supported continuity-focused response efforts designed to
          reduce operational uncertainty and stabilize affected services.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-300">
        Outcome
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-300">
        Improved incident coordination consistency, strengthened communication
        discipline, and contributed to more stable operational recovery
        processes within a high-availability environment.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-cyan-300">
        Governance & Security Relevance
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-slate-300">
        <p>
          This operational experience reinforced principles directly applicable
          to security operations, continuous monitoring, resilience planning,
          escalation governance, and incident management frameworks.
        </p>

        <p>
          The work emphasized communication accuracy, documentation discipline,
          operational accountability, and cross-functional coordination under pressure.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-cyan-300/30 bg-slate-900 p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">
        Related Resume Track
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-300">
        This case study aligns most directly with PCB’s
        Security Operations / Incident Response specialization pathway.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a
          href="/resume/security-operations"
          class="inline-block rounded-xl bg-cyan-300 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-950 transition hover:bg-cyan-200"
        >
          View Security Operations Resume
        </a>

        <a
          href="/case-studies"
          class="inline-block rounded-xl border border-cyan-300 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-cyan-300 transition hover:bg-cyan-300 hover:text-slate-950"
        >
          Back to Case Studies
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-6xl px-6 pb-4 text-center">
    <a
      href="#top"
      class="inline-block rounded-xl border border-cyan-300 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-cyan-300 transition hover:bg-cyan-300 hover:text-slate-950"
    >
      Back to Top ↑
    </a>
  </div>
</main>